2021年3月，建築裝修公司Idecor Asia Construction Limited入稟安樂戲院有限公司和百老滙戲院有限公司，追討[[太古城中心|太古城中心]]MOViE MOViE戲院的工程費，逾1,133萬元連同利息。<ref>{{cite news |title=百老匯戲院遭建築公司入稟 追逾1133萬元建築費 |url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2016621/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%99%BE%E8%80%81%E5%8C%AF%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E9%81%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F-%E8%BF%BD%E9%80%BE1133%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E8%B2%BB |accessdate=2021-03-09 |work=頭條日報 |date=2021-03-08 |archive-date=2021-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419223734/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2016621/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%99%BE%E8%80%81%E5%8C%AF%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E9%81%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F-%E8%BF%BD%E9%80%BE1133%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E8%B2%BB |dead-url=no }}</ref>

